|               |   SortPreservingMergeExec: [score@4 DESC], fetch=4                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |     SortExec: TopK(fetch=4), expr=[score@4 DESC], preserve_partitioning=[true]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                      |
