|               |         BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |           ProjectionExec: expr=[id@0 as id, answer@3 as answer, answer_embedding@1 as answer_embedding, score@2 as score]                                                                                                                                                                                           |
