|               |                 BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
|               |                   ProjectionExec: expr=[CAST(key@1 AS Int64) as id, data@0 as answer_embedding, 1 - distance@2 as score]                                                                                                                                                                                            |
